data.description: Seller is offering a chance to get into your new home with contribution of up to $10,000 toward an interest rate buydown or closing costs.   And, then you will be living in your  amazing home located in a secluded neighborhood in South Austin.  Located between Westgate and Menchaca just off Slaughter Lane you can get to just about anywhere in less than ½ hour.  HEB and Southpark Meadows are about 10 minutes away and the Univ of Texas is only 20.  And, when you come home you will have the rest and relaxation of this quiet home.  The primary suite has a walk-in closet and a full bath with vanity and sitting areas.  The in-law plan provides privacy from the secondary bedrooms (1 is currently used as an office and art/paint studio).  The wonderful kitchen has a great gas stove for cooking all your favorite meals.  This kitchen has been used to make tons of wonderful tasting cookies and pastries.  The living area with a wood burning fireplace makes a cozy space during these cold frigid days.  This  home is the total package and it is waiting for you.
